The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | Medical plan
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   Medical plan
                            
	Calcutta, Sept. 22: The government has notified a medical reimbursement scheme for its employees. The scheme will cover hospitalisation and outdoor treatment in government and select private hospitals in lieu of a monthly allowance of Rs 100.         
	Old mint         
	Eden Group has bagged the project to redevelop the Old Mint on Strand Road. The developer has tied up with the New York-based Ehrenkrantz Eckstut amp; Kuhn Architects to build a mint museum, an archive, auditorium and a heritage hotel in the 12.5-acre complex.                                                                                                                                                                         
